#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kate; offers several means of tweaking the application to behave as "
"desired. The most important ones are:"
msgstr ""
"&kate; offre plusieurs moyens de peaufiner l'application pour qu'elle se "
"comporte selon vos souhaits. Voici les plus importants :"

#. Tag: term
#: configuring.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Configuration Dialog"
msgstr "La boite de dialogue Configuration"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main configuration tool, allowing you to configure the &kate; "
"application, the editor component and the usage of plugins."
msgstr ""
"Le principal outil de configuration, qui permet de configurer l'application "
"&kate;, le composant éditeur et l'utilisation des modules externes."

#. Tag: term
#: configuring.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> Menu"
msgstr "Le menu <guimenu>Configuration</guimenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to change often used settings, and to launch the configuration "
"dialogs."
msgstr ""
"Permet de modifier les paramètres fréquemment utilisés et d'ouvrir les "
"boites de dialogue de configuration."

#. Tag: term
#: configuring.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guimenu>View</guimenu> Menu"
msgstr "Le menu <guimenu>Affichage</guimenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to split the current frame, as well as to display the icons and "
"line numbers pane for the currently edited document."
msgstr ""
"Permet de scinder le cadre actuel et d'afficher le panneau des icônes, ainsi "
"que les numéros de ligne du document en cours d'édition."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:47
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The embedded terminal uses the configuration defined in the "
#| "&systemsettings;, and may also be configured by clicking the "
#| "<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button to display a context menu."
msgid ""
"The embedded terminal uses the configuration defined in the "
"&systemsettings;, and may also be configured by clicking the &RMB; to "
"display a context menu."
msgstr ""
"Le terminal intégré utilise actuellement la configuration définie dans le "
"&centreConfiguration;. On peut également le paramétrer en cliquant avec le "
"bouton <mousebutton>droit</mousebutton> de la souris pour afficher un menu "
"contextuel."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main Configuration Dialog"
msgstr "La boite de dialogue de configuration principale"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kate; configuration dialog displays a tree of topics on the left, and a "
"configuration page corresponding to the selected topic on the right."
msgstr ""
"La boite de dialogue de configuration de &kate; affiche sur la partie gauche "
"une arborescence de thèmes et sur la partie droite une page de configuration "
"correspondant au thème choisi."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:66
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
