msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This item allows configuring &kate; for automatically saving all files with "
"unsaved changes on shutdown."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close Kate entirely when the last file is closed"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, &kate; will shutdown when the last file being edited is closed, "
"otherwise a blank page will open so that you can start a new file."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:305
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Additional Elements"
msgid "Session Elements"
msgstr "Éléments supplémentaires"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include window configuration"
msgstr "Inclure la configuration des fenêtres"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, &kate; will save the window configuration with each session."
msgstr ""
"Si cette option est cochée, &kate; enregistre la configuration des fenêtres "
"avec chaque session."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keep meta-information past sessions"
msgstr "Conserve les méta-informations des sessions passées"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When enabled, &kate; will store meta data such as bookmarks and session "
"configuration even when you close your documents. The data will be used if "
"the document is unchanged when reopened."
msgstr ""
"Lorsque cette option est cochée, &kate; mémorise des méta-informations "
"telles que les signets et la configuration de la session lorsque vous fermez "
"vos documents. Les données seront utilisées si le document est inchangé lors "
"de sa réouverture."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:328
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Delete unused meta information after"
msgid "Delete unused meta-information after"
msgstr "Supprimer les méta-informations inutilisées après"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:329
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Set the maximum number of days to keep meta information for previously "
#| "opened files. This helps keeping the database of meta information "
#| "reasonably sized."
msgid ""
"Set the maximum number of days to keep meta information for previously "
"opened files. This helps keep the database of meta information reasonably "
"sized."
msgstr ""
"Définit le nombre maximal de jours à conserver les méta-informations pour "
"les fichiers précédemment ouverts. Cette fonctionnalité permet de conserver "
"la taille de base de données des méta-informations à une taille raisonnable."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any changes to the session data (opened files and, if enabled, window "
"configuration) will always be saved."
msgstr ""
"Tout changement dans les données de la session (fichiers ouverts et, si "
"activé, configuration de la fenêtre) sera toujours enregistré."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins"
msgstr "Modules externes"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page provides a list of installed plugins for the &kate; application. "
"Each plugin is represented with its name and a short description. You can "
"check the checkbox with an item to enable the plugin it represents."
msgstr ""
"Cette page fournit une liste des modules externes installés pour "
"l'application &kate;. Chaque module externe est représenté par son nom et "
"une courte description. Vous pouvez cocher la case d'un clic pour activer le "
"module externe qu'elle représente."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a plugin provides configuration options, a section to access those will "
"appear as a child of this page."
msgstr ""
"Si un module externe prévoit des options de configuration, une section "
"permettant d'y accéder apparait sous la forme d'un double de cette page."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about the available plugins, see <xref linkend=\"plugins"
"\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Pour davantage d'informations sur les modules externes disponibles, "
"consultez <xref linkend=\"plugins\"/>."

